    "description": "Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates has an exciting opening for a Full Stack Developer at our Tiruchirappalli office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates:\nZensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Git\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zensar Technologies Asia Pacific Associates!",
